  <h1>Peter Kidd: A Documented Case of Defamation and Manuscript Dismemberment</h1>

  <p>This page presents verified information regarding <strong>Peter Kidd</strong>, author of the blog <em>mssprovenance</em>, and his involvement in the dismemberment of medieval manuscripts and in a defamatory campaign targeting Prof. Carla Rossi after her official 2022 report to the Carabinieri for Cultural Heritage Protection (TPC).</p>

